  <brief_title>Va-Sense - Bacterial Vaginosis Once A Week Screening And Treatment To Reduce Infective Complications, Abortion And Preterm Delivery In Pregnant Women With Previous Preterm Delivery</brief_title>
  <official_title>VA-SENSE - BACTERIAL VAGINOSIS ONCE A WEEK SCREENING AND TREATMENT TO REDUCE INFECTIVE COMPLICATIONS, ABORTION AND PRETERM DELIVERY IN PREGNANT WOMEN WITH PREVIOUS PRETERM DELIVERY.</official_title>
